  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2206000/extras/0a6c192bc2de654ad6c5a32c38fafec7.poster.avif?t=1692906324\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2206000/extras/0a6c192bc2de654ad6c5a32c38fafec7.webm?t=1692906324\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2206000/extras/0a6c192bc2de654ad6c5a32c38fafec7.mp4?t=1692906324\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Get in your low-poly spaceship, select a high-yield bombardment weapon, turn up the retro music volume and send the evil planet occupying civilization to the galaxy's dark ages!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2206000/extras/45aac43847ac49352f9a0bd98ad87fef.poster.avif?t=1692906324\" width=600 height=166 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2206000/extras/45aac43847ac49352f9a0bd98ad87fef.webm?t=1692906324\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2206000/extras/45aac43847ac49352f9a0bd98ad87fef.mp4?t=1692906324\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Unlock and use different space battleships with special weapons to destroy the enemies and clear the beautiful and diverse planets from exploitation and destruction.<br><br>Enjoy the retro synthwave tracks and let the bright lights take you back to the good days!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2206000/extras/9de84b6a7fec6888af367cb1b014cf7c.poster.avif?t=1692906324\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2206000/extras/9de84b6a7fec6888af367cb1b014cf7c.webm?t=1692906324\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2206000/extras/9de84b6a7fec6888af367cb1b014cf7c.mp4?t=1692906324\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Features:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 5 different spaceships with different abilities<br></li><li> Special weapons for maximum destruction<br></li><li> Unique planets<br></li><li> Retro synthwave tracks<br></li><li> Retro-space atmosphere<br></li><li> You get a complete game as in old days! No in-game transactions or DLCs.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2206000/extras/8488b6ee83396a26a22acede54a5bd25.poster.avif?t=1692906324\" width=600 height=264 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2206000/extras/8488b6ee83396a26a22acede54a5bd25.webm?t=1692906324\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2206000/extras/8488b6ee83396a26a22acede54a5bd25.mp4?t=1692906324\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
